content.p: The Faculty of Science and Engineering offer a range of exceptional programmes for study and research. We also offer Foundation programmes for students who are interested in doing an undergraduate degree with us, but first need to enhance their academic skills. To learn more about each school, including course information, job opportunities, and research priorities please visit their respective pages as below. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8001
